PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780341071
OL,3,CUK assists France in seizure of
OL,4,CRussian shadow-fleet tanker, Macron
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FBritain has assisted French forces in
OL,8,Fboarding and seizing a Russian oil
OL,9,Ftanker in the Atlantic Ocean,
OL,10,Faccording to French President Emmanuel
OL,11,FMacron.
OL,13,FThe Tagor, a sanctioned tanker, was
OL,14,Fboarded by the French navy on Sunday
OL,15,Fin international waters, Macron said
OL,16,Fin a post on X.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780341071
OL,3,CUK assists France in seizure of
OL,4,CRussian shadow-fleet tanker, Macron
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIt is the latest in a string of
OL,8,Factions by western nations to
OL,9,Ffrustrate Moscow's so-called shadow
OL,10,Ffleet, the network of tankers used to
OL,11,Fexport goods out of Russia and evade
OL,12,Fsanctions placed on the country after
OL,13,Fits full-scale invasion of Ukraine.
OL,15,FIn the social media post, translated
OL,16,Ffrom French, Macron said: "The French
OL,17,FNavy intercepted a new tanker under
OL,18,Finternational sanctions yesterday
OL,19,Fmorning, originating from Russia: the
OL,20,FTagor. Our determination is steadfast
OL,21,Fand unwavering.
OL,26,@xD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780341071
OL,3,CUK assists France in seizure of
OL,4,CRussian shadow-fleet tanker, Macron
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"This operation was carried out in the
OL,8,FAtlantic, in international waters,
OL,9,Fwith the support of several partners
OL,10,Fincluding the United Kingdom, in
OL,11,Fstrict compliance with the law of the
OL,12,Fsea."
OL,14,FHe added: "It is unacceptable for
OL,15,Fships to circumvent international
OL,16,Fsanctions, violate the law of the sea,
OL,17,Fand fund the war that Russia has been
OL,18,Fwaging against Ukraine for more than 4
OL,19,Fyears.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@EO]vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780341071
OL,3,CUK assists France in seizure of
OL,4,CRussian shadow-fleet tanker, Macron
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"These vessels, which fail to adhere
OL,8,Fto the most basic rules of maritime
OL,9,Fnavigation, also pose a threat to the
OL,10,Fenvironment and to everyone's safety."
OL,12,FFootage accompanying the post showed
OL,13,FFrench troops rappelling onto the
OL,14,Fship's deck from a helicopter, as well
OL,15,Fas night vision footage of armed
OL,16,Ftroops walking along a gangway aboard
OL,17,Fthe vessel.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
