FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780341071
OL,3,CUK assists France in seizure of
OL,4,CRussian shadow-fleet tanker, Macron
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FA Ministry of Defence spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "We can confirm that a
OL,9,Fhelicopter from onboard HMS Somerset
OL,10,Fprovided tracking and monitoring in
OL,11,Fsupport of the French operation to
OL,12,Fboard the tanker Tagor.
OL,14,F"Alongside our allies, we are stepping
OL,15,Fup our response to shadow vessels ` to
OL,16,Fchoke off the funds that fuel Putin's
OL,17,Fillegal invasion of Ukraine."
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
