FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780341071
OL,3,CUK assists France in seizure of
OL,4,CRussian shadow-fleet tanker, Macron
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FDowning Street meanwhile, rejected
OL,8,Fsuggestions the UK did not have the
OL,9,Fmilitary capability to lead an
OL,10,Foperation aimed at seizing a shadow
OL,11,Ffleet tanker.
OL,13,FThe prime minister's official
OL,14,Fspokesman said: "The UK is disrupting
OL,15,Fand deterring shadow fleet vessels and
OL,16,Ftheir harmful maritime activity, and
OL,17,Fsince October 2024 we have challenged
OL,18,Fmore than 700 suspected shadow fleet
OL,19,Fvessels.
OL,26,@vD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780341071
OL,3,CUK assists France in seizure of
OL,4,CRussian shadow-fleet tanker, Macron
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"I'm not going to comment on specific
OL,8,Foperational planning or give a running
OL,9,Fcommentary, as this could compromise
OL,10,Four ability to successfully take
OL,11,Faction against these ships and only
OL,12,Fbenefit our adversaries.
OL,14,F"But as we have said previously, any
OL,15,Ftarget ship will be individually
OL,16,Fconsidered by law enforcement,
OL,17,Fmilitary, and energy market
OL,18,Fspecialists before an operation is
OL,19,Fexecuted."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
