OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780341071
OL,3,CUK assists France in seizure of
OL,4,CRussian shadow-fleet tanker, Macron
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe UK and France have both vowed to
OL,8,Fprevent Russian-flagged ships from
OL,9,Fpassing through their waters.
OL,11,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer, in March,
OL,12,Fgave permission for British forces to
OL,13,Fseize shadow fleet vessels, leading
OL,14,Fthe ships to veer away from the
OL,15,FEnglish Channel.
OL,17,FAt the start of the year, the UK
OL,18,Fassisted the US in capturing the
OL,19,FMarinera, a Russian-linked tanker
OL,20,Ftravelling across the Atlantic from
OL,21,FVenezuela.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780341071
OL,3,CUK assists France in seizure of
OL,4,CRussian shadow-fleet tanker, Macron
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIt also helped the French capture a
OL,8,FRussian oil tanker called the Grinch
OL,9,Fin the Mediterranean.
OL,11,FKremlin spokesman Dmitry Peskov said
OL,12,Fon Monday that Russia "considers such
OL,13,Factions illegal", when asked about the
OL,14,FFrench-led action.
OL,16,F"They border on piracy," he said,
OL,17,Fadding: "We absolutely disagree that
OL,18,Fthey are being carried out in full
OL,19,Fcompliance with international law."
OL,26,@tD@WOUuD@PO]xD@AOUxD@XO]yD@IOU{D@cO]
